title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Navigating through the Orbis flying eye hospital
description:
The Orbis Flying Eye Hospital which is a MacDonell Douglas MD10 was added to MSFS 2020 as part of Sim Update 5. In this video I will show you how you can look inside the aircraft and look around at the various rooms available in the aircraft.
